→ →
To plot \(J_{n} \cdot \nabla E_{\mathrm{C}} / q\) and \(J_{p} \cdot \nabla E_{\mathrm{V}} / q\) (see Equation 78 and Equation 79), specify the corresponding keywords eJEheat and hJEHeat.

To plot \(d W_{n} /\left.d t\right|_{\text {coll }}, d W_{p} /\left.d t\right|_{\text {coll }}\), and \(d W_{\mathrm{L}} /\left.d t\right|_{\text {coll }}\) (see Equation 78, Equation 79, and Equation 80), specify the corresponding keywords eColHeat, hColHeat, and lColHeat.

