\hline\(\mu_{\mathrm{L}}\) & mumax & 1417 & 470.5 & \(\mathrm{~cm}^{2} / \mathrm{Vs}\) \\
\(\zeta\) & exponent & 2.5 & 2.2 & 1 \\
\hline
