b \rightarrow \frac{\beta E_{\mathrm{g}}}{q \lambda}
\]
where \(E_{\mathrm{g}}\) is the energy bandgap, \(\lambda\) is the optical-phonon mean free path for the carrier, and \(\beta\) is a proportionality constant. Table 91 lists the default values for \(\lambda\) and \(\beta\).

