The following example of a trap specification illustrates one donor trap level at the intrinsic energy with a concentration of \(1 \times 10^{15} \mathrm{~cm}^{-3}\) and capture cross-sections of \(1 \times 10^{-14} \mathrm{~cm}^{2}\) :
