[2] S. Senkader and C. D. Wright, "Models for phase-change of \(\mathrm{Ge}_{2} \mathrm{Sb}_{2} \mathrm{Te}_{5}\) in optical and electrical memory devices," Journal of Applied Physics, vol. 95, no. 2, pp. 504-511, 2004.
[3] D.-H. Kim et al., "Three-dimensional simulation model of switching dynamics in phase change random access memory cells," Journal of Applied Physics, vol. 101, p. 064512, March 2007.

