\end{figure}

The Gaussian time function as shown in Figure 26 is expressed as:
\[
F(t)=\left\{\begin{array}{cc}
\exp \left(-\left(\frac{t_{1}-t}{\sigma}\right)^{2}\right) & , t<t_{1} \\
1 & , t_{1} \leq t \leq t_{2} \\
\exp \left(-\left(\frac{t-t_{2}}{\sigma}\right)^{2}\right) & , t>t_{2}
\end{array}\right.
\]
where \(\sigma\) is defined by WaveTSigma.

