The exponential time function as shown in Figure 27 is expressed as:
\[
F(t)=\left\{\begin{array}{cl}
\exp \left(\frac{t-t_{1}}{t_{\exp }}\right) & , t<t_{1} \\
1 & , t_{1} \leq t \leq t_{2} \\
\exp \left(\frac{t_{2}-t}{t_{\exp }}\right) & , t>t_{2}
\end{array}\right.
\]
where \(t_{\text {exp }}\) is defined by WaveTExp.

\begin{figure}
\captionsetup{labelformat=empty}
