The cosine time function as shown in Figure 28 is expressed as:
\[
F(t)=\left\{\begin{array}{cc}
0 & t \leq t_{1}-t_{\cos } \vee t \geq t_{2}+t_{\cos } \\
\frac{1}{2} \cdot\left(1+\cos \left(\pi \frac{t-t_{1}}{t_{\cos }}\right)\right) & t_{1}-t_{\cos }<t<t_{1} \\
1 & t_{1} \leq t \leq t_{2} \\
\frac{1}{2} \cdot\left(1+\cos \left(\pi \frac{t-t_{2}}{t_{\cos }}\right)\right) & t_{2}<t<t_{2}+t_{\cos }
\end{array}\right.
\]
where \(t_{\cos }\) is defined by WaveTCos.

