This example demonstrates a KMC-MIM simulation of the leakage current in a \(\mathrm{TiN} / \mathrm{ZrO} \mathrm{O}_{2} / \mathrm{TiN}\) MIM structure. The \(\mathrm{ZrO}_{2}\) film is 9 nm thick.

